citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:12pm on
14-Nov-19.
Inspector arrived at gated facility at 2:12 pm. Called main contact number and left voicemail. Called licensee cell
number and spoke with licensee. Licensee stated they were out of state. Inspector will return at a later date.
